{"tid":2320034,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"警方呼籲市民提供觀塘屍體發現案資料","createTime":"2020-12-10T13:11:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-11T05:09:54.000Z","uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6eced0565dc3e49f3e764eb5e4f3e7d333609bc3","tid":2320034,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T13:11:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://gia.info.gov.hk/general/202012/10/P2020121000445_photo_1185121.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgia.info.gov.hk%2Fgeneral%2F202012%2F10%2FP2020121000445_photo_1185121.jpg&h=cde59ca7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://gia.info.gov.hk/general/202012/10/P2020121000445_photo_1185122.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgia.info.gov.hk%2Fgeneral%2F202012%2F10%2FP2020121000445_photo_1185122.jpg&h=436a9b44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警方呼籲市民提供觀塘屍體發現案資料（附圖）<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n  警方今日（十二月十日）呼籲市民就<span class=\"red\">九月二十三日</span>觀塘一宗屍體發現案提供資料。<br />\n        <br />\n  當日上午八時三十四分，警方接報指一名女子在油塘海岸對開海面漂浮。該名女子被救起後，現場被證實死亡。<br />\n        <br />\n  警方相信死者是一名年約二十至四十歲的女子。她身高約一點六至一點七米，中等身材，蓄短黑髮，身上有三個紋身，分別位於右肩、腹部和右大腿。被發現時身穿藍白色格仔長背心，黑色長袖外套，黑色長褲，白色平底鞋及攜有一個深啡色手袋。她身上並沒有身份證明文件。<br />\n<br />\n  警方呼籲任何認識死者或有案件資料提供的人士，請致電三六六○ 九三一六與水警港口分區雜項調查隊聯絡。<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <br />\n完<br />\n2020年12月10日（星期四）<br />\n香港時間14時51分"},{"pid":"63846b7e30d2741a2058b560cfb7ec10aa7d19cd","tid":2320034,"uid":4618,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T13:12:02.000Z","msg":"宇清<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cdadb0d8f6ddf38a9a917006f81a17f0ef32f7b","tid":2320034,"uid":7439,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T13:12:28.000Z","msg":"即刻唸起陳彥霖<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tired.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<blockquote>2019年<span class=\"red\">9月23日 <br />\n油塘</span>海面現女浮屍 未檢獲遺書<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】女子浮屍油塘海面，嚇煞釣魚郎。昨晨十一時許，一名姓劉（五十五歲）男釣客在高超道魔鬼山對開岸邊垂釣期間，發現離岸約一百米海面有人形物體漂浮，心知不妙遂報警。水警及消防輪接報到場搜索，將一名女子救起，惟經檢驗後證實她已死亡，警方其後將遺體送往西灣河水警基地。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，死者為一名年約廿五至卅歲女子，身高約一點五米，中等身材，蓄長金髮。警方在場未有檢獲遺書，暫未能確定死者身份，死因有待進一步確定，案件暫列屍體發現，交由東區警區刑事調查隊跟進。</blockquote>"},{"pid":"1d22693d03ebdec81dd8d932b71f382083f9a572","tid":2320034,"uid":352873,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T13:17:45.000Z","msg":"點解冇內衣褲？"},{"pid":"65e7023e2c392586fe307cfb5a61af873dbfdde3","tid":2320034,"uid":132810,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"63846b7e30d2741a2058b560cfb7ec10aa7d19cd","tid":2320034,"uid":4618,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T13:12:02.000Z","msg":"宇清<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T13:23:13.000Z","msg":"???"},{"pid":"2602df61f0f7f1cf5aeb3df553f2e64f98277413","tid":2320034,"uid":43861,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T13:27:39.000Z","msg":"20-40歲 咁撚大個range <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"615bd8ebf106c3c03528b2ec610d1027886e9a68","tid":2320034,"uid":136116,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4cdadb0d8f6ddf38a9a917006f81a17f0ef32f7b","tid":2320034,"uid":7439,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T13:12:28.000Z","msg":"即刻唸起陳彥霖<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tired.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<blockquote>2019年<span class=\"red\">9月23日 <br />\n油塘</span>海面現女浮屍 未檢獲遺書<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】女子浮屍油塘海面，嚇煞釣魚郎。昨晨十一時許，一名姓劉（五十五歲）男釣客在高超道魔鬼山對開岸邊垂釣期間，發現離岸約一百米海面有人形物體漂浮，心知不妙遂報警。水警及消防輪接報到場搜索，將一名女子救起，惟經檢驗後證實她已死亡，警方其後將遺體送往西灣河水警基地。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，死者為一名年約廿五至卅歲女子，身高約一點五米，中等身材，蓄長金髮。警方在場未有檢獲遺書，暫未能確定死者身份，死因有待進一步確定，案件暫列屍體發現，交由東區警區刑事調查隊跟進。</blockquote>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T13:38:08.000Z","msg":"25~30歲<br />\n浸到點先會變成咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"faa2aa9dd62910e021e21820c7b1b4a0f9d586af","tid":2320034,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"63846b7e30d2741a2058b560cfb7ec10aa7d19cd","tid":2320034,"uid":4618,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T13:12:02.000Z","msg":"宇清<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T14:43:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ed9c090ac702ba70b8dd4d0b0a0ce8662776c7e","tid":2320034,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d22693d03ebdec81dd8d932b71f382083f9a572","tid":2320034,"uid":352873,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T13:17:45.000Z","msg":"點解冇內衣褲？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T14:43:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e91f9145c7b8d30afb1b11b764a0357d5c635dd","tid":2320034,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"65e7023e2c392586fe307cfb5a61af873dbfdde3","tid":2320034,"uid":132810,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"63846b7e30d2741a2058b560cfb7ec10aa7d19cd","tid":2320034,"uid":4618,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T13:12:02.000Z","msg":"宇清<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T13:23:13.000Z","msg":"???"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T05:09:54.000Z","msg":"312！唔見人！<br />\n312！打死人！"}]}